title: [Mist Harbor, Vineyard]
description: Following the curve of the pathway that encircles the vineyard, a high stone wall creates a protective barrier that prevents pedestrians from falling off of the sharp drop of the cliffs.  Sunlight dapples the surrounding area and highlights the colorful awnings that decorate the verdant foliage to the north.
